# 📊 CARA HITUNG STOK (Jika Tidak Pakai Tabel STOCK)

Kalau mau hitung dari movement saja:

```sql
SELECT
    item_id,
    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN movement_type IN ('PURCHASE', 'PRODUCTION_IN') THEN qty
            ELSE -qty
        END
    ) as current_stock
FROM stock_movements
GROUP BY item_id;
```

